high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink that is behind you.
Pick up the egg that is in the sink to the right of the coffee mug.
With the egg in hand go to turn to your right so you are in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave.  Place the egg in the microwave on the right side.  Close the door and start the microwave.  Open the door and grab the egg.
With the egg in hand turn to your right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door.  Place the egg in the center of the second shelf.  Close the door.
